COMMENDATIONS. Commends Madison Hogan on being crowned the 100th Miss
St.Tammany Parish Fair Queen.
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Madison Elizabeth Hogan on being crowned the 100th Miss St. Tammany
3 Parish Fair Queen.
4 WHEREAS, Madison Hogan is the reigning 2025-2026 St. Tammany Parish Fair
5 Queen; and
6 WHEREAS, Madison, the 2025-2026 Fair Queen, is a resident of Mandeville,
7 Louisiana, a proud graudate of Mandeville High School; and
8 WHEREAS, at only 22 yrs old, Madison holds a Bachelor of Science degree in
9 Finance with a minor in economics from Southeastern Louisiana University; and
10 WHEREAS, she is a Southeastern Louisiana University Double Legacy Scholar and
11 an alumni of Alpha Omicron Pi sorority and the Gamma Beta Phi Society; and
12 WHEREAS, Madison competed on the Southeastern Louisiana University College
13 of Business finance competition team and also served as an ambassador for the SELU
14 College of Business; and
15 WHEREAS, she is a loyal volunteer for Our Daily Bread food pantry, and has been
16 a volunteer on Project Prom, a nonprofit started by her mother to give free prom dresses to
17 high school students who unhoused, in foster care, or otherwise in need of support; and
18 WHEREAS, Madison's goal is to attend law school and pursue a career in contract
